SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO

GO
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[PublicProvinceCity](
	[ID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](150) NOT NULL,
	[Code] [int] NOT NULL,
	[ParentCode] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Jibie] [int] NOT NULL,
	[FirstLetter] [nvarchar](50) NOT NULL,
	[LowerAcronym] [nvarchar](50) NOT NULL,
	[UpperAcronym] [nvarchar](50) NOT NULL,
	[LowerFullPinyin] [nvarchar](500) NOT NULL,
	[IsHot] [smallint] NOT NULL,
	[IsPublic] [int] NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_PublicProvinceCityNew] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[ID] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX  = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE  = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS  = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS  = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO
